trans-unit.source: Represents an ordered collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Input.InputBinding"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en ordnad samling <xref href="System.Windows.Input.InputBinding"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: All objects that derive from <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> have an InputBindingCollection named <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.InputBindings%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Alla objekt som är härledda från <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>har en InputBindingCollection med namnet <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.InputBindings%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.InputBindings%2A> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement>

trans-unit.source: All objects that derive from <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement> have an InputBindingCollection named <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.InputBindings%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Alla objekt som är härledda från <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement>har en InputBindingCollection med namnet <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.InputBindings%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.InputBindings%2A> </xref:System.Windows.ContentElement>

trans-unit.source: However, if these collections are set in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)], then the items in the collection must be derived classes of <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding> rather than direct <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding> objects.
trans-unit.target: Men om dessa samlingar är inställda i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)], objekt i samlingen måste vara härledda klasser för <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding>i stället för direkt <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding>objekt.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding> </xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding>

trans-unit.source: This is because <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding> does not support a default public constructor.
trans-unit.target: Detta beror på att <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding>stöder inte en offentlig standardkonstruktor.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding>

trans-unit.source: Therefore, the items in a InputBindingCollection that was set in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] will typically be an <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding> derived class that does support a default public constructor, such as <xref:System.Windows.Input.KeyBinding> or <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding>.
trans-unit.target: Därför kan objekten i en InputBindingCollection som angavs i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] kommer normalt att vara en <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding>härledd klass som stöder en standardmässig offentlig konstruktor, till exempel <xref:System.Windows.Input.KeyBinding>eller <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding>.</xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding> </xref:System.Windows.Input.KeyBinding> </xref:System.Windows.Input.InputBinding>
